{"tid":188080,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【母憑女貴】三圍同樣近40吋 黃婉曼話剪腳甲都要老公代勞","createTime":"2017-04-05T11:58:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-05T14:05:45.000Z","uid":25125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fc70a30c7b82bc2d41ecb15081668a656b3cefb9","tid":188080,"uid":25125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T11:58:13.000Z","msg":"【母憑女貴】三圍同樣近40吋 黃婉曼話剪腳甲都要老公代勞<br />\n建立時間 (HKT): 0405 18:02<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170405/large/1491386443_1939.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170405%2Flarge%2F1491386443_1939.jpg&h=3204efe0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n攝影：羅慧敏(蘋果日報)<br />\n<br />\n黃婉曼（Icy）、少爺占同當奴今日喺鰂魚涌宣傳ViuTV嘅娛樂節目《黑料理》，挺住5個月巨肚嘅Icy着住3吋高踭鞋，佢笑言怕肥：「好肥呀，o依家成個水桶咁，三圍幾乎一樣。」佢仲爆三圍同樣近40吋，認真驚人！<br />\n<br />\n問到老公有乜反應？佢就話：「佢冇乜所謂，唔介意，但我好介意，修身問題已經開始諗，我怕唔係BB吸收，係我成日搵BB做藉口食嘢。」佢仲話o依家好笨重，連着鞋着襪剪腳甲，都要老公代勞，佢話：「一個老婆懷孕，老公仲辛苦，我o依家母憑女貴。」咁係咪即係生女？Icy就笑話：「下次先開估。」<br />\n講番今次節目，少爺占同當奴就成日要模仿唔同嘅新聞人物，少爺占就話最難忘係扮黎明，佢話：「因為佢好多金句，冇邏輯嘅，所以好難記。我估唔到我化完妝都可以咁似，好恐怖。」而當奴就話最困難係要扮行山look嘅周潤發，笑言自己唔夠高，要用箱企高拍攝。問到佢哋有冇留意鄭俊弘劈腿事件？佢哋就話未跟進，少爺占仲話：「好似好juicy，好想八吓。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170405/large/1491386445_7e99.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170405%2Flarge%2F1491386445_7e99.jpg&h=4c521626&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n黃婉曼（Icy）、少爺占同當奴今日喺鰂魚涌宣傳ViuTV嘅娛樂節目《黑料理》。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170405/large/1491386446_f8c9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170405%2Flarge%2F1491386446_f8c9.jpg&h=e33ebe1c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n當奴同少爺占<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170405/large/1491386447_ac1b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170405%2Flarge%2F1491386447_ac1b.jpg&h=028f89c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n黃婉曼<br />\n<br />\n轉貼自: <a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/enews/realtime/20170405/56525369\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2F20170405%2F56525369&d=%2BKcr5gC3v3d6Nt4twTTWNttKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=1ad8cc4f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2F20170405%2F56525369&h=d0cc4690\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/enews/realtime/20170405/56525369</a>"},{"pid":"58d98d0af0703060ae81eb157da7d65c81a761cb","tid":188080,"uid":40839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T11:59:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6be54cae3a0b4edc8ff71d2a1df820e66e493930","tid":188080,"uid":78769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T11:59:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b24727478679b20a941020077df59eb28179d2d","tid":188080,"uid":11040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T12:01:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f162aa876f5caa5a52448928724187c3b5af9a83","tid":188080,"uid":17426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T12:01:59.000Z","msg":"等我幫佢剪"},{"pid":"e66a39872c36bddb16cdfe51653a6801e275e44c","tid":188080,"uid":25125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTim